    1137              : inline const char *EnumNameBuiltinOperator(BuiltinOperator e) {
    1138              :   if (::flatbuffers::IsOutRange(e, BuiltinOperator_ADD, BuiltinOperator_SIGN)) return "";

    1140              :   return EnumNamesBuiltinOperator()[index];
    1141              : }
